---
title: Pulled Beef, Mushroom and Redcurrant Gravy Pie with Garlic Mash and Balsamic Roasted Sprouts
description: Serve up a festive feast this winter! A comfort food classic using premium ingredients, this Pulled Beef, Mushroom and Redcurrant Gravy Pie brings the best of the British pub into your kitchen.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R37_W49_UK_SG29954-5_MAIN_high-bf57c749.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/66fbf6a79e82bf398e8fabd7-en-GB.pdf
cuisine: British
nutrition:
  calories: 900 kcal
  fat: 30.8 g
  saturated fat: 14.8 g
  carbohydrates: 108.4 g
